    "id": "improve-the-value-of-assets-cradle-to-grave-traceability-part-2",
    "title": "Improve the value of assets. Cradle to Grave traceability (Part 2)",
    "cat": "Traceability",
    "author": "Tom Meulendijks",
    "role": "Assets not only need to function properly, but they also need to be financially viable. Especially now.",
    "date": "2020-11-06",
    "cover": 6,
    "image": "",
    "preview": "",
    "glyph": "TRACE",
    "body": "",
    "summary": "The value of an asset is directly related to the information that is known about its history. That's why traceability is so incredibly important within the oil and gas industry. Assets not only need to function properly, but they also need to be financially viable. Especially now.",
    "slug": "improve-the-value-of-assets-cradle-to-grave-traceability-part-2"
